desc_long								关于这款游戏							Vertigo Void is a challenging 3D puzzle-platformer which demands a keen eye and sharp memory. As a lone astronaut, walk up walls, jump across the void of space (or fall in) and teleport your way to safety or else face the Sun's wrath. Pit your wit and skill against the Sun's encroaching menace as you chart your way through over 200 puzzling levels brimming with challenge and surprise. Loads of Game ContentOver 200 levels to completeLots of gameplay manipulating itemsAn estimated 12 hours of gameplayXbox 360 Controller supportCompatibility with Windows, Mac and Linux operating systemsCreate Your Own Levels Share your own levels with friends.Use the fully featured in-game editor to create your own levelsAn infinite number of possibilities, make the most unusual and mind-bending designs! You have access to the complete library of items available in the game. Where will your imagination take you?						
